content: Welcome to the Online Renju Class theory lesson!

Today we will continue with learning the D3 opening!
Two weeks ago, we analysed this pattern.
Today we will check another 7th move here, that is also possible. What is another 7th move here?
Yes 7. G9. But we have to emphasize in the present theory, that 7. J9 is slightly favorable for white than 7. G9.
Let's begin. Now, please press "I AM HERE" button, to show that you are here.
After warm-up your fingers, first of we will warm up our brain :-)))
